Usage: SETBACK [-C] [-H] [back message]
  Sets you back and displays messages

  If -C is given, no text will be added to your message. If -H is given,
  effect is the same as having SHOWAWAY set to OFF. If no message is
  given default message (from ScrollZ.save) is used.

See also:
  AWAYENCR
  AWAYT
  PLAYBACK
  REMLOG
  SETAWAY
  SHOWAWAY
